Title : Uroyoán Walker
Text : {{BLP sources|date=January 2015}}
[[File:Uroyoán Walker Ramos (24483275445) (cropped).jpg|thumb|Walker in 2016]]
'''Uroyoán Ramón Emeterio Walker Ramos'''{{efn|{{spanish name|Walker|Ramos|plain=yes}}}} (born in [[Brooklyn, New York]]) is a mathematician, college professor, and former President of the [[University of Puerto Rico]] (UPR). He completed a bachelor's degree in mathematics at the [[University of Puerto Rico, Mayaguez Campus]] (UPRM), and a master's and Ph.D. both from [[Louisiana State University]].<ref>{{cite web|url=http://acweb.upr.edu/docs/Junta_Gobierno/2013/Cons_Pres_UPR/Uroyoan_W_R/URWR_CV.pdf |accessdate=April 30, 2014 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140502002313/http://acweb.upr.edu/docs/Junta_Gobierno/2013/Cons_Pres_UPR/Uroyoan_W_R/URWR_CV.pdf |archivedate=May 2, 2014 }}</ref> Before his appointment as president he served at several roles including as associate dean of administrative affair at UPRM, associate director for graduate studies at UPRM, academic senator, and member of the board of trustees of the whole UPR system.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.primerahora.com/noticias/gobierno-politica/nota/conocealnuevopresidentedelaupr-971133/|title=Conoce al nuevo presidente de la UPR|work=Primera Hora|accessdate=7 January 2015|date=2013-11-19}}</ref> He was removed from office by the Board of Trustees amid [[cronyism]] scandals regarding institutional scholarships.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.telemundopr.com/noticias/Junta-de-UPR-retira-confianza-a-Uroyoan-Walker-385899781.html|title=Junta de UPR destituye a Uroyoán Walker|publisher=}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.wapa.tv/noticias/ahora/destituyen-a-uroyoan-walker-como-presidente-upr_20131122276091.html|title=Nombran nueva presidenta de la UPR|website=www.wapa.tv}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://136.145.9.247/PDF/CERTIFICACION/2016-2017/1%202016-2017.pdf}}</ref>

